exact thing I want, grab it pay for it and get home before anyone has 
realised ive moved of the couch. Yippeeeee !

       Now it has suddenly dawned on me that this appears to be a left over 
from our days as hunter gatherers. 
       Typically the women folk would spend their time forraging for tasty 
morsals. Picking and choosing the best. 
