> K CCA k GTG  L CCC l GTT  M CCG m TAA  N CCT n TAC  O CGA o TAG
> P CGC p TAT  Q CGG q TCA  R CGT r TCC  S CTA s TCG  T CTC t TCT
> U CTG u TGA  V CTT v TGC  W GAA w TGG  X GAC x TGT  Y GAG y TTA
> Z GAT z TTC
