FACE=3D"Arial">have</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">only a =
few thousand $/year and not enough</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">money for food</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">, impacting your survival</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">. When you get the stamps, you</FONT></U><U> <FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">use some of you</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">r income to pay for cable.&nbsp; You are not innocent =
because in effect you demand others to</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">subsidize your lifestyle, not merely survival. =
</FONT></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">Let's say</FONT></U><U> <FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">you could work sweeping the streets but you =
don't feel like it. To avoid starvation you come to the poorhouse. You =
are not innoc</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">ent - you =
could survive on your own but you prefer to use</FONT></U><U> <FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">the state system of =
extortion.</FONT></U><U></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">Let's say</FONT></U><U> <FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">you are filthy rich. A</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">n act of war</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">displ</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">aced =
many persons who were uninsured despite honestly trying =
to</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial"></FONT></U><U> <FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">(you usually can't get an insurance covering =
acts of war</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">)</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">. With your =
c</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">ronies you thwart a motion =
in congress to provide life-saving shelter</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial"> and food for them at your expense</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">. You are not innocent - you value your =
property above the lives of innocent persons</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">.</FONT></U><U></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">&nbsp;A landslide =
dest</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">roys homes and =
livelihood</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">s</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">.</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">The =
h</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">omes were not insured =
because of the landslide risk but the</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">ir owners bought them anyway. Now they</FONT></U><U> =
<FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">ask for state help to =
rebuild</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial"> at your =
expense</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">. You refuse. You =
are innocent. It was their fault</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">.</FONT></U><U></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">Let's say a</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">n epidemic sweeps the country.</FONT></U><U> =
<FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">Thousands</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial"> of persons who</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">chose to buy a car rather than health =
insurance</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial"> are now clamoring =
for help. You refuse and they die miserably, although there is =
enough</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">medication to help =
them. You *</FONT></U><B><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">are</FONT></U></B><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">* =
innocent! They died because of their own negligence.</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial"> They were guilty by hoping to =
use</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">violent extortion to =
pay for their mistakes.</FONT></U><U></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">There are two =
person</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">s on a sinking ship =
and one life vest. One of them grabs</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">it, depriving the other of the means of survival. He is =
guilty - infringing on the life-wish of an</FONT></U><U> <FONT SIZE=3D2 =
FACE=3D"Arial">innocent person is wrong, even if needed to save your =
own life. He should be shot for his crime. </FONT></U></P>

<P><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">But let's say both of them agree to =
a knife fight, a coin toss or other means of</FONT></U><U><FONT =
SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial"> assigning the vest. The winner is innocent =
even if splatter</FONT></U><U><FONT SIZE=3D2 FACE=3D"Arial">ed with =
