It can be a rewarding experience trying to communicate to interested and
intelligent, but otherwise immacolate parties in realtime under adverse
conditions (noise, progressive inebriation). We've been running a local
experiment for a few months now: http://mcfuturists.com/

If you can spare the time, I recommend trying to get something similiar
going in your locality. (It's even fun!).


